{"uuid":"recommended712840","createDate":1641703740000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"712840\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:06:51\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2022-01-09\",\"gameName\":\"King Exit\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/712840\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/712840/\",\"playTime\":\"25.6\",\"updateTime\":\"2022-01-09\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"25.6\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/712840\"}","title":"评测 > King Exit","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n 听说剧本超级无敌强的RPG！于是玩~\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  摸了25个小时才一周目Clear~\n </div>~有些东东没解锁~但我属于只看剧情的，所以不考虑二周目了···\n <br>\n <br>\n 这游戏过于老旧，依旧是踩地雷的遇敌方式。\n <br><span class=\"bb_spoiler\"><span>不过好在有道具和通用存档修改器···</span></span>\n <br>\n 游戏全程没有语音，毕竟是老游戏。\n <br>\n <br>\n 游戏还有各种隐藏房间，也算是各类老RPG才会有的老设定了。\n <br>\n 游戏特效算是老RPG Marker里很华丽的那种了，音乐也让人熟悉。\n <br>\n <br>\n 游戏要多存档，不然扑街了就进入剧情看不到更细节的剧情了！\n <br>\n 可惜游戏没steam成就···但游戏内有成就~\n <br>\n <br>\n 指南里有隐藏房间一览可以直接当作攻略看\n <br>\n 因为只玩过一周目，所以那个最后一个章的最强Boss外传没打！因为一周目过去会提示囚徒在挖矿进不去···\n <br>\n <br>\n 虽然RPG Maker的音乐素材都很类似，不过战斗胜利的音乐真像口袋妖怪···\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  作为HGame其实不怎么行~既没有语音角色也动不起来···\n  <br>\n  但是作为RPG剧情确实非常棒！\n  <br>\n  ~这个RPG有点让我怀念曾经66rpg的镇站之宝黑暗圣剑传说了！童年回忆之一~\n </div>虽然好像现在早没了···\n <br>\n <br>\n 剧情流水账：\n <br><span class=\"bb_spoiler\"><span>我的博客：archives/513 谁让它超过了8k字捏！然后评测塞不下！</span></span>\n <br>\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2713506527\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2713506527</a>\n <br>\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2712496813\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2712496813</a>\n <br>\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2713506974\" target